data.title: Places to visit
data.meta_description: Enjoy 400 great days out with English Heritage, from mighty castles to peaceful abbeys, and from grand country homes to atmospheric prehistoric monuments.
data.text:
A Feel-Good Summer

This summer, we've got it all: mighty castles, colourful gardens and family fun that just doesn't stop.

From a packed schedule of Legendary Events to our brand-new Summer Quests, there's something for the whole family at our sites this season.

Start your adventure

Legendary Summer Events

We've got a fantastic range of exciting legendary events featuring Romans, pirates, knights, jousts and more.

And you can keep the little ones entertained with our Summer Explorer Quests at over 29 historic sites across the country.

See What's On

New at Dover Castle

We’ve been working on a major new attraction in the northern part of Dover castle. The new experience, Dover Castle Under Siege, tells the story of the castle’s most challenging times through exciting new interactive activities, a play area and re-imagined underground tunnels.

Visit Dover Castle
